Class RoadNetwork

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.roads.model.RoadNetwork

java.io.Serializable
public class RoadNetwork
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Models a Road Network to be conflated. Contains a graph, as well as a FeatureCollection to wrap it, a spatial index, and (in the future) shape-matching stuff.

checkCoincidentEdges

public com.vividsolutions.jump.feature.FeatureCollection checkCoincidentEdges()
Checks for coincident edges (edges which are incident on the same node with the same angle at that node). These will cause problems during conflation and should not be present in the dataset. If there are no coincident segments the feature collection will be empty.

Returns:
a FeatureCollection containing any coincident edge features
